# Relay API — environment configuration. Copy to `.env` and fill in.
# The API never commits keys; `.env` is gitignored. Keys are read by the `relay` engine
# at provider-construction time (the API holds no key logic of its own).

# --- Anthropic (the loop default provider) ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- OpenAI (api.openai.com) ---
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# --- Azure OpenAI (the gpt-5.5 deployment this project ships with) ---
# When AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT is set, the engine builds an AzureOpenAI client and the
# deployment name doubles as the model id. /health reports openai as available.
# AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT=https://<resource>.openai.azure.com
# AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY=...
# OPENAI_API_VERSION=2025-01-01-preview

# --- API serving (optional overrides) ---
# Base directory for the per-run file DBs the run store creates (default: a temp dir).
# RELAY_API_STORE_DIR=
# Directory of the static frontend to mount at /app (default: repo-root app/).
# RELAY_APP_DIR=
# Comma-separated allowed CORS origins (default: localhost dev origins). Use "*" to allow all.
# RELAY_CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:8000
